Allegheny International Inc said aconsortium of banks which entered into long term and short termsecured revolving credit agreements with the company last yearhas agreed to extend a previously granted waiver of certainfinancial net worth covenants to April 29 from March 18.    The company said last week it was seeking such a waiver.    AI is currently engaged in discussions with the consortiumto extend the short term agreement beyond April 29 and expectssuch an extension will be obtained. Reuter&#3;